flowchart TB
  U[User prompt] --> R{L1 routing policy}
  R -->|bootstrap/init| B[Bootstrap]
  R -->|default non-trivial| G[GSD PM]
  R -->|UI/UX/design| X[UIUX]
  R -->|QA/testing| Q[QA]
  R -->|security| A[AppSec]
  R -->|pentest/active scan| P[ROE gate]
  B --> H[L2 hooks]
  G --> H
  X --> H
  Q --> H
  A --> H
  P --> H
  H --> E[L3 evidence]
  E --> D{gate.check}
  D -->|PASS/WARN/CONDITIONAL| Ship[Ship or handoff]
  D -->|FAIL/BLOCKED/STALE| Stop[Stop]
